  "title": "如何使用B2解锁？",
  "answer": " <p style=\"margin-top:8.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:8.0pt;margin-left:51.05pt;line-height:12.0pt;layout-grid-mode:char;punctuation-trim:leading;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Arial','sans-serif';line-height:24.0pt\">B2解锁能够帮您免除手机复杂的解锁方式，将蓝牙设备移动到手机旁，轻按手机电源，即可免密码锁手机。</p> <p style=\"margin-top:8.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:8.0pt;margin-left:51.05pt;line-height:12.0pt;layout-grid-mode:char;punctuation-trim:leading;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Arial','sans-serif';line-height:24.0pt\">使用B2智能解锁需要有一款拥有此功能的华为手机和一台蓝牙设备，蓝牙设备包括蓝牙耳机，手环等。此处以蓝牙耳机为例，设置B2智能解锁操作步骤如下：</p> <p style=\"margin-top:8.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:8.0pt;margin-left:51.05pt;line-height:12.0pt;layout-grid-mode:char;punctuation-trim:leading;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Arial','sans-serif';line-height:24.0pt\">1. 进入“设置”，选择“锁屏和密码”，进入“锁屏密码”设置您的手机密码（若您的手机已设置密码请忽略该步骤）；</p> <p style=\"margin-top:8.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:8.0pt;margin-left:51.05pt;line-height:12.0pt;layout-grid-mode:char;punctuation-trim:leading;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Arial','sans-serif';line-height:24.0pt\">2. 点击“设置” 选择“锁屏和密码”，点击进入“智能解锁，如下图所示：</p> <p style=\"margin-top:8.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:8.0pt;margin-left:51.05pt;line-height:12.0pt;layout-grid-mode:char;punctuation-trim:leading;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Arial','sans-serif';text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph; line-height:normal\">![](http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=SupportImage&imagePath=/20150917091105982001.gif)![](http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=SupportImage&imagePath=/20150917091105833002.gif)![](http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=SupportImage&imagePath=/20150917091105343003.gif)</p> <p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:21.0pt;line-height:150%;text-autospace:none;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';layout-grid-mode:line;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph; line-height:normal\">3. 输入您之前设置的锁屏密码，进入智能解锁设置界面，连接您的蓝牙设备，如下图所示：</p> <p style=\"margin-top:8.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:8.0pt;margin-left:51.05pt;line-height:12.0pt;layout-grid-mode:char;punctuation-trim:leading;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Arial','sans-serif';text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph; line-height:normal\">![](http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=SupportImage&imagePath=/20150917091105410004.gif)![](http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=SupportImage&imagePath=/20150917091105568005.jpg)![](http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=SupportImage&imagePath=/20150917091105642006.gif)         </p> <p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:21.0pt;line-height:150%;text-autospace:none;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';layout-grid-mode:line;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph; line-height:normal\">4. 选择“添加用于解锁的设备“，开启”智能解锁“，选择您第3步中连接上的蓝牙设备，如下图所示：</p> <p style=\"margin-top:8.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:8.0pt;margin-left:51.05pt;line-height:12.0pt;layout-grid-mode:char;punctuation-trim:leading;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Arial','sans-serif';text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph; text-indent:47.25pt;line-height:normal\">![](http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=SupportImage&imagePath=/20150917091105118007.gif)   ![](http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=SupportImage&imagePath=/20150917091105348008.gif)</p> <p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:21.0pt;line-height:150%;text-autospace:none;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';layout-grid-mode:line;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph; line-height:normal\">5. 全部设置完成后，您的蓝牙耳机在手机附件时能面密码解锁。</p> <p style=\"margin-top:8.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:8.0pt;margin-left:51.05pt;line-height:12.0pt;layout-grid-mode:char;punctuation-trim:leading;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Arial','sans-serif';margin-left:0cm;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph; text-indent:21.0pt;line-height:normal\">注：若有多个蓝牙设备连接到手机，这些设备都能实现B2智能解锁功能。</p>",
